{"tid":2091898,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"衝突蔓延 印度嚴查中國進口貨  莫迪刪微博「斷交」","createTime":"2020-07-03T02:43:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-03T02:47:01.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ece5fbb9144037e6d8770510012d5c027f0fde7c","tid":2091898,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:43:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200703/5WPHZPBUTMI3LUFFFFCIP36IOY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200703%2F5WPHZPBUTMI3LUFFFFCIP36IOY%2F&d=YQ8W%2FXaIcJ33D6vU0aBSBH4fze6eI6Am6%2FUgKT%2BdzFE%3D&h=e8403250\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200703%2F5WPHZPBUTMI3LUFFFFCIP36IOY%2F&h=7617bc4c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/china/20200703/5WPHZPBUTMI3LUFFFFCIP36IOY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n衝突蔓延 印度嚴查中國進口貨 <br />\n莫迪刪微博「斷交」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中印邊境軍事對峙持續，兩國緊張氣氛也從軍事蔓延至互聯網和經貿往來。印度政府繼禁止在國內使用包括TikTok（抖音海外版）、微信等59款中國手機應用程式後，總理莫迪也關閉了其開通五年的微博賬號，實行「微博斷交」。印度更對中國進口貨實施額外檢查，導致來自中國的零件卡在海關，令富士康、戴爾（Dell）的廠房生產受阻。中國商務部昨批評印方做法違反世貿組織有關規則和印方在世貿組織中的承諾，希望印方立即糾正做法。<br />\n<br />\n新浪微博表示，應印度駐華大使館要求，刪除了莫迪的微博賬號。印度亞洲新聞國際通訊社稱，莫迪已決<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n除國家主席的相片較困難」。不過，昨傍晚該賬號已被完全刪除，無法再瀏覽。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/g4FIEHrKSftun4sYJuMDI6ldFfo=/640x425/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/4QGC2ZN4VXWW5PXITE42J3U7TQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fg4FIEHrKSftun4sYJuMDI6ldFfo%3D%2F640x425%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F4QGC2ZN4VXWW5PXITE42J3U7TQ.jpg&h=a2d60208&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n莫迪實行「微博斷交」，絲毫不顧習近平面子。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/D0DF1mVZiVTFo5_eeqKIEow4QFo=/640x266/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/PDADZBRHAZD3EFKDCJ42D27UQM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FD0DF1mVZiVTFo5_eeqKIEow4QFo%3D%2F640x266%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FPDADZBRHAZD3EFKDCJ42D27UQM.jpg&h=83e9adfb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「莫迪總理」微博賬號昨已清空內容，隨後更完全消失。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/GVC-fLwm3wqump0LhgcTdcbyFyM=/640x428/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/5XJ4PSZFUI3JMYEJGAUWKRWCQE.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FGVC-fLwm3wqump0LhgcTdcbyFyM%3D%2F640x428%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F5XJ4PSZFUI3JMYEJGAUWKRWCQE.jpg&h=5f52300e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n印度據稱拖慢中國貨物進口，有快遞公司暫停中國至印度的貨運。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n開通五年 曾賀習生日<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：約翰遜、杜魯多擁百萬粉絲<br />\n<br />\n印度報業托拉斯引述執政黨人民黨全國秘書長桑托什（B.L. Santhosh）表示，莫迪退出中國社交媒體平台微博，就邊界問題、經貿問題以至「個人層面」向中國發出強烈訊息。莫迪的微博賬號在2015年5月4日開通，當時他將十天後訪華，首條微博內容為：「你好中國！期待通過微博與中國朋友們互動。」五年間他累積了逾20萬粉絲，但只發過115條微博，不算十分活躍。他<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n中印兩國部隊上月在主權有爭議的克什米爾邊境爆發流血衝突，據稱兩國近日還往印方實際控制的拉達克地區增兵。在局<br />\n。。。。。。<br />\n貿易經濟合作研究院研究員梅新育昨在微博上大動肝火：「微博斷交，有意思嗎？這政黨政治把國際競爭搞得簡直跟娃娃鬥氣一樣，讓人看輕。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/DZTQW_dhSbttzkmGz5Z6GnsLhmI=/640x448/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/677OCTVCL6HHKKANEKUTO3KO5I.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FDZTQW_dhSbttzkmGz5Z6GnsLhmI%3D%2F640x448%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F677OCTVCL6HHKKANEKUTO3KO5I.jpg&h=15d4acf2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n富士康廠無零件開工<br />\n<br />\n另外，路透社報道，逾150批富士康的貨物，包括智能手機和電子零件，都卡在欽奈口岸，導致富士康位於印度南部為蘋果和小米手機組裝的兩間廠房生產受阻。消息人士指：「富士康的處境非常不好&hellip;&hellip;許多員工待在宿舍，因為沒事可做。」美資電腦公司戴爾在印度廠房的生產也受阻，因六個裝有伺服器和桌上電腦零件的貨櫃被<br />\n。。。。。。。<br />\n卡在港口。負責監督海關部門的印度財政部官員指，目前的檢查措施只是暫時性，很快就會放寬，並指「受影響的非中國公司貨物會優先清關」。<br />\n<br />\n路透社/美聯社/中央社"},{"pid":"9415fc354b97fc36f09209cc86926ef95844a7b2","tid":2091898,"uid":78764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:45:40.000Z","msg":"加速加速<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eb119dc73f7b031280f9754315bcdf55a2012db0","tid":2091898,"uid":244818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:46:34.000Z","msg":"借個位<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 會員標籤功能 <a href=\"https://lih.kg/1880412\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1880412</a>"},{"pid":"fece7358ac40cb14d5996d813fb8e4ad43ed9db6","tid":2091898,"uid":265839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-03T02:47:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9NOESYC.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9NOESYC.gif&h=b0af813b&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}